Lee et al. [13] introduce a Predictive Clustering-based Collaborative Filtering (PCCF) that combines the Markov model and fuzzy clustering with Clustering based CF (CBCF). This method solves the issue of reduced coverage and of unstable performance by tracking the changes in

user preferences and bridging the gap between the static model and dynamic model.
Kim et al. [14] proposed a recommender system for online shopping market using GA K-means clustering. In this system, the author tries to segment the online shopping

