6 Conclusion
Recommendation system has an ability to provide personalized information on the internet. In this era of internet, lots of RSs have been developed that are based on Contentbased ﬁltering, Collaborative ﬁltering and Hybrid system and helps to reduce the problem of information overload. In this study authors found that CF recommendation system provide better recommendation but still facing problem of scalability and sparsity. So there is a possibility to improve the quality and performance of collaborative ﬁltering based recommendation system by using the fuzzy clustering and the optimization technique.
